eel .. but the bottom line is it doesn't even matter how anybody feels .. All that matters is what he wanted . And it's eating me up inside but I'm trying to make the right choice.  The choice he would have wanted... it still doesn't even feel real... since Friday I've only slept 2 hours ... I've eaten once.. but I've made sure my kids are emotionally ok and that they had a chance to go in person and say their goodbyes... the nurses told me that I did amazing while I was taking each child one by one back to visit with him .. I told them it's OK to cry.. we're crying because it's hard and sad because we loved him that much ..  I reassured them and told them they could hold his hand and talk to him .. that he could hear them .. they each said what was on their hearts.. and they all even kissed him multiple times.. I swear he knows that they were there.. my daughter even took some pictures of him so she could remember everything which I think is healthy.. but I just I'm doing my best.. I'm worried that my best is t enough ..</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pZDoR3g</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jessag87]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A moderately sized DK dump of stolen memes for these trying times 1874.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rlH1X6l</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HwM2MOs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0BNGyIO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0cLULkb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rOLp0TO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/im3HmkX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><i